      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > ATLUS [2,051 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlus">ATLUS</a> has released the third and final “Principles of RAIDOU” trailer for <em><a title="Games > RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army">RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army</a></em>, this time introducing the game’s story and characters. <span id="more-968932"></span></p><p><em>RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,571 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,270 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [160 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,038 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,994 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,150 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,270 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2288350/RAIDOU_Remastered_The_Mystery_of_the_Soulless_Army/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on June 19. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/03/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-switch-and-pc">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-details-more-characters-demons-and-progression-systems">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-th